Package MazeSolverClasses

package MazeSolverClasses
  • Class
    Description
    AStarSolver
    A class that inheriths from MazeSolver base class and implement the A* algorithm for path finding.
    AStarSolver.Heuristic
    Nested enumerator used for keeping track of the heuristic functions.
    BfsSolver
    Class that implements the Breadth-First Search.
    DeadEndFillingSolver
    Class that implements the dead-end filling algorithm.
    DfsSolver
    Implements the depth-first search algorithm.
    DfsSolver.Wrapper
    Wrapper class that stores a boolean.
    LeeRoutingAlgorithm
    Implements Lee's algorithm, one of the Routing algorithms.
    MazeSolver
    An abstract class from which all maze solvers will inherit.
    RecursiveSolver
    Recursive Solver Algorithm.
    RecursiveSolver.Wrapper
    Wrapper static class that has a boolean that indicate if a path has been found or not, so other threads can stop, if this value is set to true.
    SolverType
    Enumerator that stores the type of Maze Solver Algorithms that the program implements, so the user can select from them.
    TremauxSolver
    This class implements the Tremaux Algorithm.
    WallFollower
